UK: Portugal issues small additional fuel oil tender.Portugal issues small additional fuel oil tender.Portugal's state utility Electricidade de Portugal (EdP) has tendered to buy one 30,000 tonne cargo of heavy fuel oil in August, traders said on Tuesday.The tender, due to be awarded on Wednesday, was a surprise to some traders who said the company had already awarded six cargoes for August.The latest tender is for delivery between August 27-30.-- Matthew Jones, London Newsroom +44 171 542 8980